# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok bayern munich midfielders michael ballack and owen hargreaves are injured and will miss wednesday 's champions league match against french side lens .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (ii / injure-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Michael"
                              :op2 "Ballack")
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (t / team
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Bayern"
                                          :op2 "Munich"))
                              :ARG2 (m / midfielder)))
                  :op2 (p2 / person
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Michael"
                              :op2 "Hargreaves")
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 t
                              :ARG2 (m2 / midfielder)))))
      :op2 (m3 / miss-02
            :ARG0 a2
            :ARG1 (m4 / match-03
                  :ARG0 t
                  :ARG1 (t2 / team
                        :ARG0-of (c / champion-01)
                        :mod (l / league)
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "France")))
                  :ARG2 (l2 / lens
                        :mod (s / side))
                  :time (d / date-entity
                        :weekday (w / wednesday)))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok former us president bill clinton , who is a un special envoy on tsunami recovery efforts in the indian ocean , expressed shock monday at the killing of ## aid workers in sri lanka .
# ::alignments
(e / express-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Bill"
                  :op2 "Clinton")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "United"
                              :op2 "States"))
                  :ARG2 (p2 / president)
                  :time (f / former)
                  :ARG0 p)
            :ARG1 c
            :ARG2 (e2 / envoy
                  :ARG1-of (s / special-02
                        :polarity -)
                  :topic (e3 / effort-01
                        :ARG1 (r / recover-01
                              :ARG2 (t / tsunami))
                        :location (o / ocean
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Indian"
                                    :op2 "Ocean")))))
      :ARG1 (s2 / shock-01
            :ARG0 (k / kill-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (w / work-01
                              :ARG1 (a / aid-01)))
                  :location (c2 / country
                        :name (n4 / name
                              :op1 "Sri"
                              :op2 "Lanka")))
            :ARG1 p)
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m / monday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok george w. bush said thursday that if the child of a relative or friend were raped and asked him about abortion , he would hope to respond with sympathy and would advise that `` it 's up to her '' whether to have the operation .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "George"
                  :op2 "W."
                  :op3 "Bush"))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (h / hope-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (r / respond-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :manner (s2 / sympathize-01)))
            :op2 (a2 / advise-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (t / truth-value
                        :polarity-of (h2 / have-03
                              :ARG0 (p2 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (h3 / have-rel-role-91
                                          :ARG1 (o / or
                                                :op1 (p3 / person
                                                      :ARG0-of (h4 / have-rel-role-91
                                                            :ARG1 p
                                                            :ARG2 (r2 / relative)))
                                                :op2 (p4 / person
                                                      :ARG0-of (h5 / have-rel-role-91
                                                            :ARG1 p
                                                            :ARG2 (f / friend))))
                                          :ARG2 (c / child))))))
            :condition (a3 / and
                  :op1 (r3 / rape-01
                        :ARG1 p2)
                  :op2 (a4 / ask-01
                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (a5 / abort-01)
                        :ARG2 p2)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))

                              :ARG1 w3
                              :ARG3 r)))))

                  :mod (m2 / military)
                  :poss c2)

                        :ARG0 p2
                        :ARG1 (r3 / rock)

            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

# ::id 7 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok tengku jafar sways and moans the name of allah , dips the blade of his <unk> knife into a freshly blessed bottle of mineral water and makes the pronouncement that fatimah has been waiting to hear : some of her ## missing relatives are still alive .

                                    :ARG1 p2
                                    :ARG2 (r / relative))
                              :ARG1-of (m / miss-01))))
            :mod (s2 / still))
      :ARG2 (a / and
            :op1 (l2 / laugh-01
                  :ARG0 p2)
            :op2 (n2 / name
                  :op1 "Allah"))
      :ARG3 (b / blade
            :part-of (k / knife
                  :poss p2))
      :location (b2 / bottle
            :ARG1-of (b3 / bless-01
                  :manner (f / fresh))
            :consist-of (w / water
                  :mod (m2 / mineral)))
      :ARG1-of p
      :ARG0 p2
      :ARG1-of (w2 / wait-01
            :ARG2 (h2 / hear-01
                  :ARG0 p2)))

                  :ARG0-of d2

      :ARG1 (e / expect-01

                                          :value 3)))

      :ARG1 (h / high-02
            :ARG1 (p2 / price-01
                  :ARG1 (f / futures
                        :mod (r / rubber))
                  :location (c / country
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Singapore")))
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (f2 / friday))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (v / volume
                        :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (s2 / small)
                              :ARG3 (m / more)
                              :ARG2 h)))
            :ARG1 p2
            :ARG3 m))

# ::alignments
(g / give-01
      :ARG0 (o / organization
            :ARG0-of (r / regulate-01)
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "EU")))
      :ARG1 (g2 / go-ahead-19
            :ARG1 (c2 / company
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Royal"
                        :op2 "Philips"
                        :op3 "Electronics"))
            :ARG2 (p / purchase-01
                  :ARG0 c2
                  :ARG1 (c3 / company
                        :ARG0-of (s / supply-01
                              :ARG1 (m / magnet))
                        :ARG1-of (m2 / major-02)
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c4 / company
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "United"
                                          :op2 "States"
                                          :op3 "of"
                                          :op4 "America")
                                    :ARG0-of (m3 / make-01
                                          :ARG1 m))
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c5 / corporation
                                          :mod (g3 / general)))))
                  :ARG0-of (b / boost-01
                        :ARG1 (u / unit
                              :mod (e / equipment
                                    :mod (m4 / medicine))
                              :poss c2)))
            :mod (m5 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (e2 / euro)))
      :ARG2 c2
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / tuesday)))
